CR Lead Opportunity Procedure Instance Record	CR Lead Opportunity Procedure Instance Record	Lead Opportunity Procedure Instance Record	##			Handles the capture and subsequent development of a customer Lead Opportunity	IO	IO			O	I				O
			Customer Reference			Reference to the associated customer (can currently be a person or a company)	I	IO			O	I				O
			Customer Campaign Reference			Reference to the customer campaign generating the lead (if the opportunity is generated by a campaign)	I	IO			O	I				O
			Customer Campaign Type			The type of campaign (e.g. cross-sell, up-sell, retention)	I	IO			O	I				O
			Customer Campaign Version Number			The version number of the campaign (used to track campaign impact)	I	IO			O	I				O
			Product/Service Type			The type of product or service identified in the Lead Opportunity	I	IO			O	I				O
			Product Instance Reference			Reference to a specific product instance if the lead is an up-sell to an existing product agreement	I	IO			O	I				O
			Employee/Business Unit Reference			Employees involved in capturing the Lead Opportunity	I	IO			O	I				O
			Lead Opportunity Description 			Narrative/description of the opportunity if available	I	IO			O	I				O
			Date/Time/Location			Date and time and the location the Lead Opportunity was captured	IO	IO			O	I				O
